    <a name="introduction"></a><strong>Introduction.</strong><br />
    Subject to the requirements of applicable law, we endeavour to adhere to a consistent set of practices 
    concerning the use of your personal information. By accepting the Privacy Policy and the User Agreement 
    you expressly consent to the storage of your personal information (as provided by you) on our servers 
    located in the Federal Republic of Nigeria. This Privacy Policy is effective on March 1st, 2009.
    <br/><br/>
    <a name="collation"></a><strong>Collation.</strong><br />
    We may collect and store the following personal information:
    <ul>
    <li>Email address and other physical contact information</li>
    <li>Depending on the service used, financial information, such as credit card or bank account numbers</li>
    <li>Information based on your activities on this Site (such as bidding, buying, selling, item and content you generate or that relates to your account)</li>
    <li>Shipping, billing and other information you provide to purchase or ship an item</li>
    <li>Computer sign-on data, statistics on page views, traffic to and from the Site</li>
    <li>Other information, including IP address and standard web log information, and 
    supplemental information from third parties.</li>
    </ul>
    <br/>
    <a name="use"></a><strong>Use.</strong><br />
    Our primary purpose in collecting personal information is to provide you with an improved and 
    personalized experience. In doing this we may combine your information with information we collect 
    from other companies. We don't sell or rent your personal information to third parties for their 
    marketing purposes without your explicit consent.
    <br/><br/>
    You agree that we may use your personal information to:   
    <ul>
    <li>Provide the services and customer support you request;</li>
    <li>Resolve disputes, collect fees, and troubleshoot problems</li>
    <li>Prevent potentially prohibited or illegal activities, and enforce our User Agreement</li>
    <li>Customize, measure, and improve our services and the Sites' content and layout</li>
    <li>Tell you about targeted marketing, service updates, and promotional offers based on 
    your communication preferences; and compare information for accuracy, and verify it with third parties.</li>
    </ul>
    <br/>
    <a name="disclosure"></a><strong>Disclosure.</strong><br />
    We may disclose personal information to: third party service providers who help our business, 
    prevent potentially illegal acts, respond to legal requirements, enforce our policies, respond 
    to claims that a listing or other content violates the rights of others, or protect anyone's rights, 
    property, or safety. We may also share your personal information with other business entities, 
    should we plan to merge with or be acquired by that business entity. In any case, you will recieve 
    prior notice if your personal information will be used contrary to this policy.
    <br/><br/>
    Without limiting the above, we will not otherwise disclose your personal information to law enforcement, 
    government officials, or other third parties without a subpoena, court order or substantially similar 
    legal procedure, except when we believe in good faith that the disclosure of information is necessary 
    to prevent imminent physical harm or financial loss or to report suspected illegal activity.
    <br/><br/>
    We cannot guarantee the privacy or security of your information when divulged to trading partners and 
    therefore we encourage you to evaluate the privacy and security policies of your trading partner before 
    entering into a transaction and choosing to share your information. However, to help protect your privacy, 
    we allow only limited access to other users' contact, shipping and financial information in order to 
    facilitate your transactions. When users are involved in a transaction, they may have access to each 
    other's name, User ID, email address, and other contact and shipping information. Furthermore, in all 
    cases, you must give others a chance to remove themselves from your database and a chance to review 
    what information you have collected about them.
    <br/><br/>
    You agree to use user information only for: ${appName} transaction-related purposes that are not
    unsolicited commercial messages; using services offered through ${appName} and other purposes that
    a user expressly chooses.
    <br/><br/>
    <a name="spam"></a><strong>Spam.</strong><br />
    You are not licensed to add other users to your mail list without their express consent. To report 
    ${appName} related spam or spoof emails please forward the email to spam@looseboxes.com. You may
    not use our mail tools to send content that would violate our User Agreement.
    <br/><br/>
    <a name="security"></a><strong>Security.</strong><br />
    Your information is stored on our servers located in the Federal Republic of Nigeria. We use lots of 
    methods to protect your personal information against unauthorized access. However, third parties may 
    unlawfully gain access to your personal information. Therefore, although we work very hard to protect 
    your privacy, we do not promise, that your personal information or private communications will always 
    remain private.
    <br/><br/>
    <a name="cookies"></a><strong>Cookies.</strong><br />
    Cookies are small files placed on your hard drive which contain information generally used by the 
    originator. We use "cookies" on certain pages of the Site to help analyze our web page flow, customize 
    our services, measure promotional effectiveness, and promote trust and safety.<br/>
    A few important things you should know about cookies are that: 
    <ul>
    <li>We offer certain features that are only available through the use of cookies. </li>
    <li>We use cookies to help identify you and maintain your signed-in status. </li>
    <li>Most cookies are are automatically deleted from your hard drive at the end of a session. </li>
    <li>You are always free to decline our cookies if your browser permits, although doing so may interfere 
    with your use of this site. </li>
    <li>You may encounter cookies from third parties on certain pages of the Sites that we do not control. 
      (For example, if you view a web page created by another user, there may be a "cookie" placed by that 
    web page.)</li>
    </ul>
    <br/>
    <a name="closing_an_account"></a><strong>Closing an Account.</strong><br />
    Upon your request, we will close your account and remove your personal information from view as soon 
    as reasonably possible, based on your account activity and in accordance with applicable law. We do 
    retain personal information from closed accounts in order to comply with law, prevent fraud, collect 
    any fees owed, resolve disputes, troubleshoot problems, assist with any investigations, enforce our 
    User Agreement, and take other actions otherwise permitted by law.
    <br/><br/>
    <a name="miscellaneous"></a><strong>Miscellaneous.</strong><br />
    <ul>
    <li>Your User ID is displayed throughout ${appName} and is therefore available to the public. Therefore, 
      if you associate your name with your User ID, the people to whom you have revealed your name to will 
    be able to personally identify your ${appName} activities.</li>
    <li>If your password is compromised for any reason, immediately notify ${appName} and change it. Please
    note that if you dont, you may be subject to legalling binding actions taken on your behalf.</li>
    <li>You change most of your personal information by logging into the Site. Once you make a public 
    posting, you may not be able to change or remove it.</li>
    </ul>
    <br/>
    <a name="amendments"></a><strong>Amendments.</strong><br />
    We may amend this Privacy Policy at any time by posting the amended terms on the Site. All amended 
    terms automatically take effect 28 days after they are initially posted on the Site. In addition, we 
    will notify you in accordance with your Notification Preferences.<br />
